data.description: CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS Take a look at this custom built home on 2 1/2 acres of land. This 4 bed 2 1/2 bath home has all the room your looking for. The kitchen has brick accents, and all oak cabinets. The Family room has a fireplace and a private phone nook. The Master bedroom is on the first floor, and the other three bedrooms  are upstairs. A large screened in porch, and a double carport. A detached 24x30 garage with workshop. Dont wait, Make this your home today. Note. seller to have carpets professionally cleaned 10/27/23.  All details deemed accurate, if important buyer to verify
